features: 【Your Travel Baby Cleaning Solution】Our 7-in-1 upgraded bottle brush set includes an detachable baby bottle brush, nipple brush, straw brush, soap dispenser, bottle drying rack, and organizer case. Deep clean even the narrowest openings and crannies with ease, without damaging interior surfaces, all while using the convenient 1.7oz soap dispenser.

【Convenient Built-in Bottle Drying Rack】 Designed with 4 branches and an upgraded draining tray, our travel baby cleaning set can hold baby bottles, nipples, sippy cup lids, breast pump parts, making it perfect for working moms. With this lightweight and small set, it is baby travel essential and portable on the go.

【Safe & Durable Material】 Made of high-quality PP and liquid silicone material, our brush set is safe and BPA-free. The less sticky bristles do not collect dirt like sponges and nylon brushes, providing you with peace of mind every time you use them. The set is dishwasher safe, and the silicone bottle brush head is detachable and boilable.

【Multi-purpose Usage】Our travel bottle cleaner kit can clean not only baby bottles, nipples, and straws, but also containers with hard-to-reach nooks and crannies, such as insulated water bottles, wine glasses, glassware, and dishes. Easily clean and maintain the brush set by rinsing it under running water after use and letting it air dry.

【Small Size & Portable】 The hook design of the brush handle allows you to hang the brush in the kitchen or store it in the storage box. The portable design of the storage box (7.2*4.5*2 inches) make it easy to store in your diaper bag or luggage, so you can take it with you wherever you go.

【Great Gift Idea For Moms】Leucite travel cleaning set makes for an exquisite gift for baby showers, pregnant women, and new moms. Suitable for parent-child travel, family, airports, nursery rooms, and other outdoor activities, gift a sweet and considerate present for those who matter most.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Grandma's House!
reviews.reviewText: We are very pleased to have this portable brush and drying rack set for our grandchildren's drinking cups and bottles. The brushes are of good sizes and the drying rack works well for a few items at a time. Each item in the cleaning set is dishwasher safe if placed on the top rack. The entire set is portable, so we will loan it out to the parents if they need something like this when traveling. (Or we will get them a set of their own!). This would make a nice gift for new parents or grandparents.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This set is perfect for traveling when you want to keep bottles clean when drying. Everything folds up compact, and it's light weight enough to throw in the diaper bag or in a suitcase. I like how the brush is made of sillicone, so you can boil it easily to sanitize and keep clean. I was able to clean multiple Avent bottles on a recent trip and used the rack to set them out to air dry. Very happy with this set!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well designed portable set
reviews.reviewText: I have been using the 7 in 1 bottle brush cleaner set helping with my new grandson and am pleased with several aspects of this set. The silicone bottle brush and shaped nipple brush work very well, and being made of silicone that stays cleaner and is boilable is a great idea. The straw brush is also good for cleaning standard anti-colic bottle parts. The travel case is a good size for packing into a diaper bag. I do not think all breast pump parts would fit in this small container (at least the ones my daughter has will not). Neither of us has tried the small soap dispenser yet. I would recommend this very nice, portable set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This item looks like the perfect addition needed when traveling with a new born. The drying prongs are tall and sturdy and should at together fit two bottles. Which I think is great for rotating how many you bring. The kit includes what feels like silicone bottle brushes which is nice because they are easier to clean and faster to dry. It’s compact form makes it easy to storage in your car, Dipars bag or luggage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the perfect little travel set. It opens and closes smoothly, it’s not too large, it’s light weight and they have cool colors. I love that it can all go into the dishwasher! We haven’t done that yet but anything that can go in the dishwasher is great, a life saver one might say. The bottle drying rack that lifts up from the inner cover lifts up and goes back down easily.It comes with all you really need! Different brushes for different bottle parts and a soap dispenser! The bottle brush stores in two pieces, I was afraid it would be tough to get undone to close it all back up but I have to say I am impressed. No issues so far and I don’t foresee any!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact and light
reviews.reviewText: I got this to dry bottles for bottle feeding kittens. I really like the soft silicone brushes, which feel gentler than the traditional bottle brushes. When I don’t have a litter, I have found it is also good for drying silicone zip top baggies. While I don’t travel with a litter of kittens, the compact nature of a travel item means it stores any nicely till the next kitten season.

reviews.reviewText: I like this because it does not take up so much space on the kitchen counter top and easy to carry about ! It has everything to clean bottles and hold them to dry! It is a great set box to keep at home and carry about

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Not much to say
reviews.reviewText: As the headline state, there's not much to say on this. Material is nice and works, everything works as it should and it is very simple to use. This is a must have if you plan to or travel frequently with a new born and need to clean his or hers bottles. Took us awhile but we finally got one and I regret not getting one earlier.
